                                                    <term key="column" ana="#column">columns</term> with one <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጢር፡</foreign> 
                                                    <term key="bird" ana="#bird">bird</term>, two <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዱራ፡</foreign> birds,
                                                    and four <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጕዕራ፡</foreign> birds
                                                    atop, presumably intended to contain part of the Eusebian prefatory material, but 
                                                    (originally) left empty.</desc>
                                            </decoNote>
                                            
